instalar servidor apache ( a su eleccion )
    - php  5.3.2+
    - mysql ( opcional )

descargar e instalar Composer
    https://getcomposer.org/doc/00-intro.md

descargar e instalar Zend
	composer require zendframework/zendframework1  ( Version 1.12 )


instalar y/o habilitar  controlador oci8  ( oracle )
    ;extension=php_oci8.dll
    ;extension=php_oci8_11.g.dll
